{
  "stem": "27335.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what I-- I had to add about, uh-- the-- or-- Joe's brothers and sisters, as an equal-- equal citizen, there was no such thing as-- well, I- I- I'd be wrong to say that there was no-- no-- some sign of anti-semitism hidden there, because it is-- a-a-always-- always infiltrated.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what it-- uh, has absolutely n-n-no effect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes-- I remember one time where a teacher came in from-- from-- from Romania, from Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See-- many escaped after the First World War, and came to Romania-- occupation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many, many, many of the intellectuals-- and in all, who was there? -two teachers, and one of-- one of the bellmen in the Catholic church, and he was really wild man.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He hated everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he especially hated the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But sometimes, sometimes, it broke out from him-- but that was no-- that was no-- no-- ground for it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No-- nobody fell for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are happy with that, and we-- we are really happy that the Jews go in the store, and- and we have-- a-- a place to go for grocery, and for yard stuff, and so on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was really an objectively-- it was an-- an assimilation on the part of the-- of the Jewish-- Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had no- no special-- special desires, or anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were satisfied that as they- as they were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see-- they took-- they placed and they served the peasantry, so to-- so to say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was agricultural, see, and uh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, well-- well, there were in the- in the village surroundings, the- the big land estate-- there were a few big, uh, landowners with 2,000 acres-- and-- and there was only 6,000 acres.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- so-- and they were the ones, then, who brought out some anti- anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
